{"surah_number":109,"arabic":" الكٰفرون","latin":"Al-Kāfirūn","transliteration":"Al-Kafirun","translation":"Orang-Orang kafir","total_ayat":6,"location":"Makkiyah","ayat":[{"surah_number":109,"ayat_number":1,"arabic":"قُلْ يٰٓاَيُّهَا الْكٰفِرُوْنَۙ","kitabah":"قُلْ يٰٓاَيُّهَا الْكٰفِرُوْنَۙ","latin":"Qul yā ayyuhal-kāfirūn(a).","translation":"Katakanlah (Nabi Muhammad), “Wahai orang-orang kafir,"},{"surah_number":109,"ayat_number":2,"arabic":"لَآ اَعْبُدُ مَا تَعْبُدُوْنَۙ","kitabah":"لَآ اَعْبُدُ مَا تَعْبُدُوْنَۙ","latin":"Lā a‘budu mā ta‘budūn(a).","translation":"aku tidak akan menyembah apa yang kamu sembah."},{"surah_number":109,"ayat_number":3,"arabic":"وَلَآ اَنْتُمْ عٰبِدُوْنَ مَآ اَعْبُدُۚ","kitabah":"وَلَآ اَنْتُمْ عٰبِدُوْنَ مَآ اَعْبُدُۚ","latin":"Wa lā antum ‘ābidūna mā a‘bud(u).","translation":"Kamu juga bukan penyembah apa yang aku sembah."},{"surah_number":109,"ayat_number":4,"arabic":"وَلَآ اَنَا۠ عَابِدٌ مَّا عَبَدْتُّمْۙ","kitabah":"وَلَآ اَنَا۠ عَابِدٌ مَّا عَبَدْتُّمْۙ","latin":"Wa lā ana ‘ābidum mā ‘abattum.","translation":"Aku juga tidak pernah menjadi penyembah apa yang kamu sembah."},{"surah_number":109,"ayat_number":5,"arabic":"وَلَآ اَنْتُمْ عٰبِدُوْنَ مَآ اَعْبُدُۗ","kitabah":"وَلَآ اَنْتُمْ عٰبِدُوْنَ مَآ اَعْبُدُۗ","latin":"Wa lā antum ‘ābidūna mā a‘bud(u).","translation":"Kamu tidak pernah (pula) menjadi penyembah apa yang aku sembah."},{"surah_number":109,"ayat_number":6,"arabic":"لَكُمْ دِيْنُكُمْ وَلِيَ دِيْنِ ࣖ","kitabah":"لَكُمْ دِيْنُكُمْ وَلِيَ دِيْنِ ࣖ","latin":"Lakum dīnukum wa liya dīn(i).","translation":"Untukmu agamamu dan untukku agamaku.”"}]}